      <div class="msgContentFrame">We all know content is a big part of the problem, and hopefully it is coming. What are your top three suggested improvements to quickly improve your FFXIV experience. <br /> <br />My top three are: <br /> <br />1. Auction House or some sort of highly organized search feature for both buying and listing items for sale. <br />2. Equalize SP gains for DoW and DoM so that it is similar to how DoH and DoL SP works. EP, EM, T, VT, IT mobs = X SP for all active contributors + bunus for being in PT or performing certain Battle Regimen. <br />3. UI Improvements. Improved response times, changes to the amount of menus to complete certain task, and most of all: Improved targeting!! <br /></div>
