      <div class="msgContentFrame">1. <b>NPC-quests.</b> Something that will keep me engaged in the world. Speaking to floating rocks isn't the same and it never will be. <br /> <br />2. <b>Auction House</b>  I don't understand why SE is so stubborn about this. It doesn't make game design sense. It doesn't make financial sense. It doesn't make any kind of sense whatsoever. The retainer system will never ever be as quick and easy as an AH would. SE invented the AH in MMOs so you'd think they'd be proud of it. This isn't an evolution. <br />I haven't met ONE person online who actually prefers the system to an AH so WHY oh <i>WHY</i> would you as a company make that decision? <br /> <br /> <br />That's it. These improvements would make this one of the best MMOs. I personally can't think of anything else and am perfectly happy with everything else in the game.</div>
