      <div class="msgContentFrame">Here's 6 lol <br /> <br /> <br />1. Party Function~ This has to be the redone completely all aspects. Why? b/c I have partied now many times and have only got 2 ranks.. The Xp/Sp ratio is horrible and the fact that i have to run up and hit the mob to get ANY decent sp is inane. I had ALL mage jobs leveled in XI and most enjoyable part was being able to sit back relax and leave the beating of mobs to Tank/DD's. You are trying to hard to make everyone envolved. I have now grinded by myself on mobs now for 3 levels and it is getting old. A. b/c it is hard to find mobs that give good sp/xp B. when you do find them mobs they don't give better sp/xp then the light blue conned mobs. Example: Thistletail Marmot Blue Con gives better sp/xp then a Fairie Fungar that cons Yellow. can you explain that too your communitie? Then there is no auto attack why? I am sorry but the last thing i wanna do is hit a button a frickin hundred times every 2 minutes lol.. how am i supposed to chat let party members know what I am thinking or what to do next if i am the leader?? or how to setup skill chains if there is any... we tried in a pt for hour the other night to get one to work lol... and still have not got it yet.. Keep things simple like in XI B/c remember one thing developers as the game progresses so does the job and who wants to be 70 conjurer in the middle of a pt beating on mob to get sp and let a tank die and here him/her bitch for a hour about how u let them die. I could keep going but I dont have the time for it.  <br /> <br />2. Menu System~ Too elaborate... there is tooooo many sub menu's. Make it simple and effective like in XI. Example: Bazzar menu set unit price/ sale price what is the need for this? Just have it where ya put the price and how many like in XI simple but yet very effective.... I dont need to take it our for dinner i need to buy stuff and go or sell stuff and sit there bazzaring. I think most get the hint in this.... Simple and fast not slow and elabrorate.  <br /> <br />3. Retainer System/No AH~ Ok fact is there has to be a AH not havening this function alone will kill this game. But I do think the retainer system should be kept for bazzaring high dollar items that cost too much to put on the AH. I mean personally I have been running around for 13 levels in RSE before I cound find someone that had gear that fitted me and I could use. AND still using the RSE staff gdi... And idc about the stupid look up retainers on website function THIS was not expressed on the box and what if i like to play fullscreen? I gotta log out and log back in lol Frick that....  <br /> <br />4. Gear Damage~ Do away with it period lol what were u really thinking??? I just camped ten days to get a Speed Belt to have it fall apart 2 days later. Were you japs high when you thought of this?  <br /> <br />5. UI~ Well i will just say it is junk redo it period. it is cool that you can move things around but I cast a spell and it takes 5 seconds to go off? wth Should have kept it simple. I kinda get the feeling you are trying to cut off third party tools like windower. lol the windower was built by the fans does that tell ya something? Do what makes the fans happy. b/c in the end we fund your jobs w/o us you have no jobs/meaning to life. AND get rid of active/passive......... /heal Yes Pleaes!  <br /> <br />6. Chat/PT search~ No &lt;pos&gt; No /sea all 13-16?? really?? no Ctrl R to reply to ppl are you making this hard on purpose? or more time consuming so it takes longer to do things? These things should have been mandatory with the game launch, not patches 2 months later if we even get them then... I shouted for 2 hours the other night to get a pt of 3 going @@! it didnt take this long to get a dunes PT going even before level sync in XI lol.  <br /> <br />7. Crafting~ I didnt do crafting in XI till 4 yrs after starting the game and only then b/c i had all missions/levels done. I understand some ppl only like to craft and this section will gladly need opinionated on. idk nothing about crafting atm hence i give no opinion on it. <div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>75 Thf,Whm,Nin,Blm,Rdm,Brd   RoZ~0  CoP~0 ToAU~0  <br />WoTG Current Bastok Rank 10 Cooking 106+3  <br />Late Night Dynamis Can i Have It orz  <br />AF2 Thief 3/5 Thief 4 life <br />Banned 6-7-09  Reason &quot;Irregular Credit Card Activity&quot;</div></div>
