      <div class="msgContentFrame">3 Huh? Well, never said they had to be narrow or specific... <br /> <br />1) <b>Squash the Random Bug</b> <br /> <br />No, I don't mean bug as in a glitch or otherwise program bug. I mean bug as in your sick desires to make everything random. Crafting results are far too random and inconsistent. It makes crafting tedious, irritating and frustrating to level let alone make things to sell. Getting random recipes from the guildleves don't help us to discover new recipes that you decide to put into the game and <b>good freaking God</b> it is NOT fun having the skills you equip for crafting randomly pop up instead of being always available. But it's not just in crafting... <br /> <br />Gathering... WTF? You seem to have implemented a new &quot;You sense item X above/right at/below where you are &lt;gathering&gt;&quot; message but.... it does absolutely NO GOOD.  I can mine Item X and it will tell me I sense Item X somewhere. If I move the slider, I will get item Y and it will tell me I can find item Y somewhere even if it's where I was told Item X is. I want to be able to say, OK self, I need 3 stacks of Item Z. I want to be able to go somewhere, gather, and come back with 3 stacks of Item Z within a reasonable amount of time. Getting tons of random junk and 0 of Item Z in 4 hours of gathering is NOT my idea of an enjoyable experience. <br /> <br />Levequests... Ummm... I am a 19 Conj/16 Thaum. Why is it that I have received many quests offering Thaum Marks, but not a single one offering Conjurer Marks? Why on my solo guildleve am I fightning groups of cactaur who can 1000 needles me for 1000 damage when I have 600HP? Why do HIGH LEVEL EXTREMELY AGGRESSIVE MOBS RANDOMLY spawn in the spawn tables of low level mobs? Especially when those spawn points are RIGHT near LEVEQUEST mobs which results in making the whole levequest virtually impossible because the zones are not spacious enough to go around them? This can be less of a problem in some areas of the desert, but in the Black Shroud... good GOD.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>行く河の流れは絶えずしてしかも元の水にあらず。よどみに浮かぶ泡沫はかつ消えかつ結びて久しくとどまりたる例なし世の中にある人と住みかも全くのごとき。　－方丈記</div></div>
